<div id="wb_element_instance1871" class="wb_element" style=" line-height: normal;"><h1 class="wb-stl-heading1" style="text-align: justify;">Par 70, yardage 6,800. The Royal Aberdeen Balgownie Links is one of the oldest courses in the world and, as such, has attracted many top players over the years. Even some of them have found it to be a tough test and, for many, it is a perfect example of the exacting nature of links golf. The 18th is a par-4 measuring 434 yards and is reckoned to be one of the best finishing holes anywhere in Scotland. There's plenty of trouble awaiting a wayward tee shot and, even if you find the fairway, the approach is far from easy.</h1>

<h1 class="wb-stl-heading1" style="text-align: justify;">Originally founded in 1780 as the Society of Golfers at Aberdeen, the Royal Aberdeen Golf Club is the sixth oldest golf club in the world.  Before or after a round, golfers can review an number of historical golf memorabilia in the clubhouse to add to your experience.</h1>

<h1 class="wb-stl-heading1" style="text-align: justify;">Malmaison Aberdeen is a vibrant jewel nestled in the heart of Scotland's Granite City. Situated just moments from the city center, this hotel offers 79 stylish rooms and suites. Each boasts expansive beds, invigorating power showers, and artistic decor that embodies comfort and chic.</h1>

<h1 class="wb-stl-heading1" style="text-align: justify;">Elegance merges effortlessly with modernity, offering a unique ambiance. On your upcoming golf retreat to northeastern Scotland, we extend a warm invitation to experience the unmatched fusion of comfort and style at Malmaison Aberdeen.</h1>

<h1 class="wb-stl-heading1" style="text-align: justify;">Allow us to enhance your golfing escapade, providing you with a welcoming sanctuary upon your return. Malmaison Aberdeen becomes more than a hotel; it becomes a partner in your journey, a place where memories are forged.</h1>

<h1 class="wb-stl-heading1" style="text-align: justify;">Indulge in the blend of luxury and design, a retreat that transcends mere accommodation. Let Malmaison Aberdeen be your haven as you explore the captivating fairways of northeastern Scotland. Your golfing adventure will be heightened by the unmatched comfort and sophistication that only we can provide.</h1>
